{"tid":2402421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警司沒出示委任證 襲警案被告誤以為是暴力藍絲廢老","createTime":"2021-02-10T11:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T13:50:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d3aa7993b1e72e4e3c97166a49080c0f5a129715","tid":2402421,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"警司陳子良（右）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1beFkGd2QBhLWFbzmQUNmWaPLUk=/802x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/THELWCOQJNAQZLUJOTEXE4RIJI.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1beFkGd2QBhLWFbzmQUNmWaPLUk%3D%2F802x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTHELWCOQJNAQZLUJOTEXE4RIJI.jpeg&h=209abb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府去年2月徵用美孚饒宗頤文化館翠雅山房作武漢肺炎隔離營，遭過千名美孚街坊遊行反對，有人以雜物堵路。警方事後以在公眾地方造成阻礙及襲警罪名拘控四人，其中三人的案件今於九龍城裁判法院開審。辯方盤問當日有份拘捕被告的警司陳子良，指陳當日並無展示委任證；被告憑其外表，以為陳只是一般「暴力藍絲」及「暴力廢老」，並指陳使用過份武力制服被告。<br />\n<br />\n當日為西九龍刑事應變大隊總部指揮官的警司70637陳子良供稱，他接到情報指當日會有人進行示威活動，於是連同8名便裝同袍到美孚港鐵站外一帶埋伏。其間他發現包括次被告在內的多名人士搬動垃圾桶進行堵路，遂隨即上前拘捕次被告。<br />\n<br />\n陳指次被告當時作出強烈反抗，多次拳打他的頭，令其口罩、眼鏡及帽子全數掉落地上。雙方糾纏，直至其他警員到場協助，始能將次被告制服。<br />\n<br />\n代表次被告的大狀郭憬憲盤問陳時則指，次被告當時根本不知道陳的警察身份。陳庭上回應謂：「我有講警察停手。」郭追問當時次被告如何回應，陳稱「佢只係係咁講粗口」，例如講「X你老母」。郭再問為何次被告要一邊打陳一邊講「X你老母」，陳回應謂「唔知」。<br />\n<br />\n郭續指，陳一直扯著次被告連帽衞衣上的帽子，令次被告不能呼吸。陳稱沒有想過，又指「佢好大力反抗，我冇見過透唔到氣嘅人咁大力」。郭聞言隨即指出：「你面前嘅膠板如果令你透唔到氣，你都會好大力打開佢。」陳對此未有正面回應。審訊明天繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/SWJPPB4CMNAZBO2XUS22HSUK6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FSWJPPB4CMNAZBO2XUS22HSUK6A%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=17aba7c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FSWJPPB4CMNAZBO2XUS22HSUK6A%2F&h=b4733ad9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/SWJPPB4CMNAZBO2XUS22HSUK6A/</a>"},{"pid":"bae44792fdf8f2deeb83334b72e38792c533aa14","tid":2402421,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b05a42dc0074ec48808e10004ccdf9603a7c8e","tid":2402421,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8540ea5e53b49d927c9f009038a7a0ac6f858c95","tid":2402421,"uid":84176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"個個都話自己係警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9815aa679beae9c7738f5734ab1e3b7cfb6e8505","tid":2402421,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"//郭續指，陳一直扯著次被告連帽衞衣上的帽子，令次被告不能呼吸。陳稱沒有想過，又指「佢好大力反抗，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我冇見過透唔到氣嘅人咁大力</span></span></strong>」//<br />\n<br />\n陳警司點解你成日會見到啲透唔到氣嘅人喺度反抗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe6fe5f2f6b485ce5ac859502fa39937407bb28","tid":2402421,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9815aa679beae9c7738f5734ab1e3b7cfb6e8505","tid":2402421,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"//郭續指，陳一直扯著次被告連帽衞衣上的帽子，令次被告不能呼吸。陳稱沒有想過，又指「佢好大力反抗，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我冇見過透唔到氣嘅人咁大力</span></span></strong>」//<br />\n<br />\n陳警司點解你成日會見到啲透唔到氣嘅人喺度反抗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:48:19.000Z","msg":"俾佢試吓唞唔到氣，睇吓佢反唔反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c351ac5c0954a37b25228ad448c275c53636ff","tid":2402421,"uid":288675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"左面勾結外國勢力Wo"}]}